{"tid":48451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"笨豬跳繩索過長　巴西男頭部直撞地面亡","createTime":"2016-12-21T05:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T07:17:35.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c420ebd595a7ac7514eaa27cae36dc4dd444b844","tid":48451,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:42:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eY6vgpjJsGc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DeY6vgpjJsGc&d=pN576KrB24uCbIBGki5f25kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=38fdb98d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=eY6vgpjJsGc</a> <br />\n<br />\n巴西一名36歲男子日前在當地玩高空彈跳時，因為繩索過長，跳下時頭部撞到地面死亡，其妻兒在旁目擊他遇險一刻。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://imguol.com/c/bol/brasil/c6/2016/12/19/18dez2016---fabio-ezequiel-morais-35-anos-pouco-antes-de-fazer-salto-de-bungee-jump-segundo-a-mulher-do-serralheiro-a-corda-usada-no-salto-era-maior-que-os-40-metros-de-altura-da-1482158144399_615x470.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimguol.com%2Fc%2Fbol%2Fbrasil%2Fc6%2F2016%2F12%2F19%2F18dez2016---fabio-ezequiel-morais-35-anos-pouco-antes-de-fazer-salto-de-bungee-jump-segundo-a-mulher-do-serralheiro-a-corda-usada-no-salto-era-maior-que-os-40-metros-de-altura-da-1482158144399_615x470.jpg&h=8e208c27&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20161221/420_a3877cafab495d1a8c356965e18bf9c3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20161221%2F420_a3877cafab495d1a8c356965e18bf9c3.jpg&h=425a3b5b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n36歲的莫賴斯（Fabio Ezequiel de Moraes）在聖保羅一座40公尺高的橋，與兄弟及妻兒玩高空彈跳，有消息指由於營運的公司錯誤計算繩索長度，莫賴斯撞向地面，送到附近的醫院傷重不治。 <br />\n莫賴斯原本打算與兒子雙人跳，但最後打消念頭決定單人跳，兒子幸免於難。 警方帶走高空彈跳的器材調查。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"4b0ea358d6f2308da2a6e6fb82d94c8515703a8e","tid":48451,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:43:17.000Z","msg":"lm"},{